long_description: at orchard chiropractic & physiotherapy we are committed to your health, wellness, and performance goals by providing a variety of specialized services. we offer a variety of manual chiropractic adjusting techniques and soft-tissue techniques (such as graston technique, shockwave therapy, and active release techniques) to provide effective healthcare solutions for a large variety of conditions. physiotherapists are highly trained health professionals with a focus on injury rehabilitation. physiotherapists are movement specialists that use a hands-on approach to help you restore, maximize, and maintain movement and function throughout your life. everyone can benefit from massage. kinesiologists are human movement specialists who are university educated. they design and implement exercise programs which are based on in-depth postural analysis, functional movement screens, and strength/flexibility assessments. contact our kelowna office today. since 2008, orchard chiropractic & physiotherapy has been serving kelowna and the surrounding communities as a premier family wellness and sports injury care centre.
